  * [Yeti] Handling context
    Ensure basic extensions are recognized to select a context (*.ad?, *.[ch]).

----------
-- Bugs --
----------

  * [Yeti] Storage_Error with Browse
    Found a scenario: when Hypergrep is just started, unselect the checkbox
    "Scan Only Project Files", click Browse button, select a dir with mouse
    (don't type a directory !), click OK, select the directory with the mouse
    in the combobox, overwrite it by typing "f", click Start.
